    • Constructor Detail

      • MatchResult

        public MatchResult(java.util.ArrayList<Player> redTeam,
                   java.util.ArrayList<Player> blueTeam,
                   double odds,
                   WinningTeam winner,
                   int redChange,
                   int blueChange,
                   MatchResultStatusEnum recordStatus)
        Initialize a match result class that is stored in the mapdb database to record a match. The parameters of this class cannot be changed, as doing so would create bad side effects for the mapdb database. To change parameters, generate a new match and replace the record of the old one.
        Parameters:
        redTeam - An array list of players on the red team.
        blueTeam - An array list of players on the blue team.
        odds - The odds of red team winning the match. (ex. 0.57)
        redWin - A boolean that is true is red won the match
        redChange - An integer representing the change in rating for members of the red team.
        blueChange - An integer representing the change in rating for memebers of the blue team.
